g" alt="" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;aspect-ratio:4/3;display:block" /><img src="/articles/inside-the-formic-automation-community-event-at-land-o-frost-how-full-service-aut/1746389751-lof_automateshowcase-9-1.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;aspect-ratio:4/3;display:block" /></div>
